MTT Virtual Display Driver (third-party/mtt-vdd/)
================================================================================
LuminalShine bundles a copy of MikeTheTech's Virtual Display Driver as the
default virtual-display backend. The driver is distributed under the MIT
License (see third-party/mtt-vdd/LICENSE for the full text).

Project page : https://github.com/VirtualDrivers/Virtual-Display-Driver
Authors      : MikeTheTech, Jocke (zjoasan), and contributors
Driver build : 11.30.4.434 (December 2024 release)
Code signing : SignPath Foundation, via GlobalSign Code Signing CA 2020.
               No additional certificate setup is required at install time.

This driver is the recommended backend on supported Windows builds.
LuminalShine retains optional integration with SudoVDA for users on Windows
Insider preview builds where MTT VDD compatibility is unverified.